A [[exchange|currency_exchange]] site where bitcoins may be bought using cash transfer methods [[UKash]] (EUR), HalCash (Hal-Cash) (EUR) and Neteller instant money transfers (EUR).

The price at which the bitcoins are bought is relative to the BTC/EUR market rate at the leading exchange.

There may be restrictions when attempting to redeem UKash (EUR) vouchers from one country with a merchant in another.  This includes Germany (1.1), some vouchers from Brazil and possibly elsewhere as well.

The service is attended to during weekday business hours, Central European Time (CET).

##History

The service was revealed on August 2, 2012 (2.1).

